library(tibble)
library(tidyverse)
library(moderndive)
library(ggthemes)
library(patchwork)
library(skimr)
set.seed(12345)
# fake data
fd <- tibble(x1 = rnorm(n = 500,
                        mean = 500,
                        sd = 100),
             x2 = rnorm(n = 500,
                        mean = 500,
                        sd = 50))
# wider SD
p1 <- ggplot(fd,
             aes(x = x1)) +
  geom_histogram(color = "white",
                 boundary = 500,
                 binwidth = 25) +
  scale_x_continuous(limits = c(200,800))

# narrower SD
p2 <- ggplot(fd,
             aes(x = x2)) +
  geom_histogram(color = "white",
                 boundary = 500,
                 binwidth = 25) +
  scale_x_continuous(limits = c(200,800))
